 Gen-4 can generate complex scenes with multiple moving elements and\nrealistic physics. The training process involves massive datasets of high-quality images\nand videos paired with descriptive text, teaching models to associate visual concepts\nwith linguistic descriptions and generate novel content that matches human artistic\nintentions and aesthetic preferences."},"757":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-74","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"Stable Diffusion Training"},"758":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-75","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"DALL-E 3 Technical Report"},"759":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-76","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"Video Generation Models"},"760":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-77","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"Diffusion Model Tutorial"},"761":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-78","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"Computer Vision Basics"},"762":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-79","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence#-learning-resources","content":"Image Generation Guide"},"763":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence-80","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intelligence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/ai-visual-intellige