rds without needing to build complex payment infrastructures themselves."},"2166":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-182","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#astra-payments","content":"No Cut-Off Times: Transfers are processed instantly, regardless of weekends or holidays, with no waiting for ACH settlement windows."},"2167":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-183","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#astra-payments","content":"No Prefunding Required: Astra handles settlement and reconciliation automatically, so businesses don't need to pre-fund accounts or manage operational complexity."},"2168":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-184","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#astra-payments","content":"Security and Compliance: The platform includes built-in compliance, fraud detection, and PCI-compliant SDKs for secure transactions."},"2169":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-185","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#cost-structure","content":"Industry-Standard Fee: For instant \"push\" payments to external debit cards, Astra typically charges an industry-standard fee of 1.5% per transaction."},"2170":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-186","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#cost-structure","content":"Cost-Plus Pricing: Astra offers cost-plus pricing designed to scale with customer growth, making it less costly than traditional wire transfers and competitive with other instant payment providers."},"2171":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-187","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#cost-structure","content":"Custom Fees: Businesses can optionally apply programmatic fees to each transaction to generate additional revenue."},"2172":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-188","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#cost-structure","content":"No Additional Infrastructure Fees: There's no need for additional compliance, capital commitments, or operational overhead for instant payments."},"2173":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-189","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Feature"},"2174":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-190","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Astra Payments Details"},"2175":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-191","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Speed"},"2176":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-192","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Instant (real-time, 24/7, including weekends/holidays)"},"2177":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-193","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Method"},"2178":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-194","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor#summary-table-1","content":"Push-to-card (Visa Direct), API integration"},"2179":{"id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor-195","page_id":"/docs/comparisons/payment-processor","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comparison